Privacy Policy
I. GENERAL PROVISIONS
We kindly request that you thoroughly read this privacy statement. It provides important information about how your personal data may be handled. 
        When you use the app, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agreed to these terms. By accessing or using the app, you consent to the processing 
        of your personal data in accordance with this privacy statement.
At
Begamob Global
(referred to as "our company," "we," or "us"), we prioritize your privacy. This Privacy Statement ("Privacy Statement") 
        outlines our commitment to safeguarding your data and delineates the kinds of information we may collect when you utilize one or more of our mobile applications 
        (referred to as "the App" or "our App").
II. INFORMATION COLLECTION
2.1 Data You Provide
When you interact with our App, we request and gather specific personal details about you. This information is essential for the proper execution of the agreement between us.
Personal Details: Voluntarily provided data for tracking, storing records, and managing them.
Registration and/or Account Details: Email, Facebook ID, or Google ID, depending on the App's configuration.
Content Details: Photos, images, videos, audio files, documents, and other uploaded data.
2.2 Automatically Processed Data
While using the App, some information about your device and usage patterns may be automatically processed. This data is usually non-personal and is processed for app improvement.
Automatically processed data may include:
Advertising ID, device brand/model, browser type/version.
IP address, MAC address, IMEI, OS version, and locale data.
Cookies and similar technologies.
III. DISCLOSURE OF YOUR INFORMATION
3.1 Third Parties Channels
We do not lease or sell your personal data but may share some information with third parties like Google, Facebook, and Apple for advertising and analytics purposes.
3.2 International Data Transfer
Your data may be transferred across countries due to our global operations. We ensure proper security measures and comply with relevant data protection laws.
IV. EXERCISING YOUR RIGHTS
4.1 Data Processing Rights
Request access or copies of personal data.
Request modifications or corrections.
Restrict processing in certain circumstances.
Request deletion of personal data.
4.2 Security
We use industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data. However, no method is 100% secure.
4.3 Information Relating to Children
Our App is not intended for individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from them.
V. PRIVACY POLICY MODIFICATIONS
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of such updates.
